"Open Accessibility Settings..." = "打开辅助功能设置...";

/* Welcome */
"I live in the menu bar and keep your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working — then let it sleep when they stop.\n\nA checkmark in the menu bar means Keep Awake is on." = "我住在菜单栏里，会在 Codex 或 Claude Code 工作时让你的 Mac 保持唤醒，工作结束后再让它休眠。\n\n菜单栏中的勾选标记表示 Keep Awake 已开启。";

/* About manual */
"Keeps your Mac awake so long coding jobs finish while you're away." = "让你的 Mac 保持唤醒，这样即使你离开，长时间的编码任务也能完成。";
"How it works" = "工作原理";
"It's automatic" = "全自动";
"While Codex or Claude Code are working, your Mac stays awake. When they finish, it sleeps as usual. You don't have to do anything." = "当 Codex 或 Claude Code 工作时，你的 Mac 会保持唤醒；它们结束后，Mac 会照常休眠。你无需做任何事。";
"Turn this on to keep your Mac awake no matter what, until you turn it off." = "开启此项可让 Mac 始终保持唤醒，直到你将其关闭。";
"Blocks the keyboard during a run so a pet or child can't interrupt it. Press ⌘⌥⌃L to unlock." = "在任务运行时锁定键盘，防止宠物或小孩打断它。按 ⌘⌥⌃L 解锁。";
"Keep working with the lid shut. Use it on a desk only — it pauses if your Mac gets too hot." = "合上盖子也能继续工作。仅限在桌面上使用——如果 Mac 过热会自动暂停。";

