"Battery" = "电池";
"Low battery warning" = "低电量提醒";
"Off" = "关闭";
"Notification banners" = "通知横幅";
"Optional. Sound alerts still work without banners." = "可选。即使没有横幅，声音警报仍会工作。";
"Test alert sound" = "测试警报声音";
"Test" = "测试";
"Display" = "显示器";
"Turn off screen after" = "关闭屏幕时间";
"Never" = "永不";
"3 minutes" = "3 分钟";
"5 minutes" = "5 分钟";
"10 minutes" = "10 分钟";
"15 minutes" = "15 分钟";
"Lid closed" = "合盖";
"Run this only with your Mac on a desk. In a bag it can't shed heat and may overheat. It pauses on its own if it gets too hot, but don't rely on that." = "仅在 Mac 放在桌面上时使用。放进包里会无法散热，可能过热。它会在过热时自动暂停，但请不要依赖这一点。";
"Turn off lid-closed and remove its admin access." = "关闭合盖模式并移除其管理员权限。";
"Remove" = "移除";

/* Button states */
"Allow" = "允许";
"Open Settings" = "打开设置";
"Not Set" = "未设置";

/* Lid-closed failure */
"Lid-closed mode not enabled" = "合盖模式未启用";
"It needs a one-time admin approval. Try again when you're ready." = "它需要一次性的管理员授权。准备好后请再试一次。";

/* Thermal back-off */
"Your Mac is getting warm, so I paused lid-closed work to protect it. It resumes automatically once it cools." = "你的 Mac 有点热，我已暂停合盖运行以保护它。降温后会自动恢复。";

