"Keyboard locked" = "键盘已锁定";
"Vibe Coding Guard is blocking the keyboard. Press ⌘⌥⌃L to unlock." = "Vibe Coding Guard 正在锁定键盘。按 ⌘⌥⌃L 解锁。";

